{"type": "article", "id": 26340, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-05-04T07:19:01Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 27126, "name": "Kea"}, {"id": 27127, "name": "Wago"}, {"id": 27128, "name": "EVA light"}, {"id": 27129, "name": "Catch-All"}, {"id": 27130, "name": "Oss Craft Distillery"}, {"id": 27131, "name": "Iratzoki & Lizaso"}, {"id": 27132, "name": "Creativeans"}, {"id": 14845, "name": "Foster + Partners"}, {"id": 15397, "name": "Grovemade"}, {"id": 20036, "name": "Kind"}, {"id": 27133, "name": "Alexandra Kehayoglou"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 48, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702151007JVrv8Qm2xWEwF3YU.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p>\n<h2>Kea collection by Iratzoki &amp; Lizaso</h2>\n<p class=\"\">喜欢朴素的木质家具？不妨来看看 <a href=\"http://iratzoki-lizaso.com/\">Iratzoki &amp; Lizaso</a> 工作室为 <a href=\"http://alki.fr/\" target=\"_blank\">Alki</a> 设计的这个名为 Kea 的系列。无论是锻铁弯曲的弧度还是嵌入木材的设计，橡木与铁艺展现出的统一感是它最大的特点。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105051qAitmBlhEH2PIKrN.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76405868\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105052ChlBSdHI4uEUrPNz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.13814181\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105052lviN8akHEIPxeKqJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73227384\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021050530qJGl34WNfFRVkHy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.10635697\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105053KQaCOYBqHJ2h1ldS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.07701711\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105054ErZwSXuAo7OJx9gj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.21149144\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Wool Rug by Alexandra Kehayoglou</h2>\n<p class=\"\">无论你之前见过多少条漂亮的毯子，当看到艺术家 <a href=\"http://www.alexkeha.com/\">Alexandra Kehayoglou</a> 制作的这些羊毛毯时或许还是会在心底惊呼一声“美如画”。采用回收材料手工制成的毯子每一块都是独一无二的，好像是在房间里放置了一个梦幻花园，给人一种沉浸式的体验。根据大小，艺术家需要经过一周甚至两个月才能制作完工。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105054bCOa321JptQSXe0z.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105054uHk0CpzSZXRYaPlU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021050555ewpTr6k80hZcR2S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105056vSlY6nOw5Q9MfsPo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105056prbRcYtx47Lhl8zu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105057NzJvGRnfLxBEryUP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Wago by Creativeans</h2>\n<p class=\"\">爱带着食物到处走的吃货们，<a href=\"http://creativeans.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Creativeans</a> 设计的推车桌（trolley table）算是一大福音。如果你看到这个词觉得陌生也不必惊慌，因为这台 Wago 可能是世界上第一台能当桌子使用的推车了。当然，没有人说手推车里不能放食物以外的东西，但随着风和日丽的天气越来越多，还有什么比它更适合一场野餐之旅呢？</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070210505734au5gAwn2DJMvKf.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105058532ovCVSI7Bdwl6p.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021050588jDpOFsourWYZV5T.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105058g401Dyc3KmoQFNp8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021050598zmoxPLjalN7tJMW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105059lsSdH0geG136rmNa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76095238\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>EVA light by Foster + Partners</h2>\n<p class=\"\">这款 <a href=\"http://www.fosterandpartners.com/\">Foster + Partners</a> 为米兰的照明品牌 <span class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.lumina.it/\" target=\"_blank\">Lumina</a> 设计的 EVA 台灯不光在外形上带来惊喜，对光源的设计也让人眼前一亮。在圆柱形的玻璃外壳中，底部装有一个面光源（COB）的 LED 灯， 经过顶部圆锥体的反射，散发出温暖的光芒，整体的造型看起来就好像在玻璃罩中点燃一根蜡烛。另一个比较有意思的细节则是台灯底部传感器，它其实是调光器，可以通过滑动自由调节亮度。</span></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105100ifCYJTUzNG04verS.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105101gOnvEP0SZA5JVykU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105101shdexIbPk2rU9pAB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105102qpFLE0ObXlBRghZC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105102raXNnf6i8zcxJeSj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105102LAqNQHRE6DjsaF7O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56234719\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Catch-All by Grovemade</h2>\n<p class=\"\">来自美国俄勒冈州波特兰的品牌 <a href=\"http://grovemade.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Grovemade</a> 以手工制作的木制科技产品外壳以及桌上配件而出名。对于打算利用墙面的收纳控来说，他们新推出的 Catch-All 可以满足你的需求。内嵌的羊毛防止物品产生划痕，盒子底部还安装了三个黄铜挂钩，是挂钥匙的完美选择。它售价为 149 美元，可以通过<a href=\"http://grovemade.com/product/walnut-catch-all/?initial=203\">链接</a>购买。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105103p2URyqgTJQiL6MnD.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105103hvFGB5lR8Q1TkgsV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105104DN0Gu2thUo3pOZrv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105104jChbMyF8xqJvi97g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105105UpbNz6S3tCdOuvek.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105105ZbsRcaDA2reqz6wL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68888889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Oss Craft Distillery by Kind</h2>\n<p class=\"\">阿夸维特酒是斯堪的纳维亚地区的一种烈酒，挪威的设计公司 <a href=\"http://www.kindnorway.com/\">Kind</a> 在接到 Oss 工艺酿酒厂的委托之后，设计了以黑色为基调的外包装，传递出北欧的凛冽感以及神秘的气质。然而，当你旋转酒瓶就能发现背面印刷着色彩鲜艳的图像，这种强烈的反差正如 Kind 形容的斯堪的纳维亚人：就像椰子一样，外表坚硬冰冷，内在柔软甜蜜。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105106UTCGazjXSeAQEZo3.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105106PfmhbiJTxpsn9Clo.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105106A7Mg6v3frqcpU401.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105107yJrNKYDhM10Ltgpm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105107tyaM3m7ST0FBoflW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021051087nlUPw8XY5ZNCMFH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}